{
  "texts": [
    "It's evident that both the variety and quantity of ideas generated by the LLM exceed those generated by the TRIZ expert.",
    "Additionally, the two experts evaluated the quality of the ideas based on Section title \"Quality\".",
    "Figure 11 demonstrates box plot diagrams showing the quality of the ideas generated by the model and those generated by TRIZ experts for the exact same case study.",
    "In the third case study, the TRIZ expert proposed two primary ideas to address the design issue, but one was rejected by evaluator 1 for not effectively resolving the contradiction.",
    "It is evident that the ideas generated by the LLM vary widely in quality, ranging from very high-quality ideas to low-quality ones."
  ]
}